@33  = ~That is a wise and beneficial decision for all concerned.~
@34  = ~As thou wish, <CHARNAME>. I shall wait for thee here.~
@35  = ~As thou wish, <CHARNAME>. We shall wait for thee here.~
@36  = ~If thou dost no longer desire my companionship, then so be it. I shall not force myself where I am not wanted.~
@37  = ~If thou dost no longer desire my companionship, then so be it. I shall not force myself where I am not wanted. Come Minsc, we will continue on ourselves.~
@38  = ~Why dost thou ask this of me, <CHARNAME>? Surely one as wise as thou canst see that I cannot do thy bidding.~
@39  = ~Why dost thou ask this of me, <CHARNAME>? Surely one as wise as thou canst see that we cannot do thy bidding.~
@40  = ~I shall wait for thee at the Friendly Arm Inn. It is a safe enough place for a weary traveler in thy strange lands.~
